&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/USA-NEW-ORLEANS-AUGUST-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8480&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/USA-NEW-ORLEANS-AUGUST-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- NEW ORLEANS- AUGUST-OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;150&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/MEDIA-GAYOT-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-8481&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/MEDIA-GAYOT-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- GAYOT- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;94&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The cuisine of New Orleans is like none other, influenced by France, West Africa, Spain and the Caribbean. Dedicated to his Louisiana roots, Chef John Besh has created a classic French menu with a haute-Creole twist, which earned him Best Restaurateur of the Year for 2015 by Gayot, placing on Gayot 2015 Top 40 Restaurants in the U.S. since 2006, and winning a AAA 4 Diamond Award. The restaurant is located in the central business district of New Orleans in a beautiful building with high ceilings and elegant chandeliers, creating a lovely dining ambiance. Impeccable service with Southern charm and hospitality round out the experience. Business casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book via email at august@chefjohnbesh.com.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In the notes section of the booking form please mention: This is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. We understand that a glass of sparkling wine and special amuse per guest will be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: The restaurant will contact you 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

